text: Józef Kocyan (born 14 February 1946) is a Polish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Poland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Wisła
